{"lemma":"جُرْحَيْ","slug":"جُرْحَيْ","root":"ج.ر.ح","root_slug":"ج-ر-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ر-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جُرْح","root":"جرح","pos":"V","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n5456","n5457"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wound","examples":[{"text":"و من يبذر الشوك يجن الجراح","english":"For he who sows the thorns reaps the wounds"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to wound, to hurt","examples":[{"text":"أَسَاءَ ٱسْتِعْمَالَ السِّكِّينِ فَجُرِحَ.","english":"He mishandled the knife and injured himself."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to wound much"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to invalidate (testimony)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to challenge (witness)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَرَحَ (jaraḥa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5456","headword_ar":"جَرْحٌ","root":"jrH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n5457","headword_ar":"جُرْحٌ","root":"jrH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraHa","text_ar":"جَرَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wound;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaroHN","text_ar":"جَرْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in its original acceptation; but some of those skilled in the science of lexicology say that the former is employed to denote the effect produced upon bodies by iron instruments and the like; and the latter, that produced upon objects of the mind by the tongue: (MF:) the pl. of the former is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juruwHN","text_ar":"جُرُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajoraAHN","text_ar":"اَجْرَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is a pl. of pauc.] (S, L, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraAHN","text_ar":"جِرَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, A, L;) but the second of these is of rare occurrence, (K,) only used in poetry: (S, L:) [respecting the third, see what follows:] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraAHapN","text_ar":"جِرَاحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juroHN","text_ar":"جُرْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraAHN","text_ar":"جِرَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraAHaAtN","text_ar":"جِرَاحَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraAy^iHu","text_ar":"جَرَايِحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraAHN","text_ar":"جِرَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a coll. gen. n., of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiraAHapN","text_ar":"جِرَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.; or, accord. to Az, this last has not a sing. sense, as Lth asserts it to have, but is a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juroHN","text_ar":"جُرْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijaArapN","text_ar":"حِجَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HajarN","text_ar":"حَجَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAlapN","text_ar":"جِمَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamalN","text_ar":"جَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibaAlapN","text_ar":"حِبَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolN","text_ar":"حَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.)"}],"source_refs":["MF","S","L","K","Msb","A"]}]}}